!!! html
%html
  %head
    %title hooppps | a mobile dribbble browser
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'browser'
    = javascript_include_tag 'browser'
    = csrf_meta_tag 
    / %meta{:name => 'viewport', :content => 'user-scalable=no, width=device-width'}
    %meta{:name => 'viewport', :content => 'width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0; user-scalable=no;'}

  %body  
    #browser-content
      #call-to-demo
      #frame.scrollable
        #track
          #header
            %h1.hooppps
              %a{:href => '/'} hooppps
            %a.nav{:href => '#nav'} nav
            != back_button
            /%a.back_button{:href => 'javascript:window.history.back()'} Back
          = yield
          = render :partial => "shared/nav"
      #right
        #heading
          %h1 hooppps
          %p 
            A free open-source mobile 
            %a{:href => "http://dribbble.com", :target => '_blank'} dribbble
            browser
        .browser-about
          %h2 Why hooppps?
          %p
            Because I wanted to look at sweet dribbble shots on my phone while waiting 
            in line at the grocery store.
        .browser-about
          %h2 How do you get it?
          %p
            You already got it! There’s nothing to download, hooppps is a webapp. Just revisit 
            this URL on your mobile browser and bookmark this baby!
          %p.not-just-iphones **Not just for iPhones.
        .browser-about
          %h2 Who made this awesomesauce?
          %p
            hooppps was made by 
            %a{:href => 'http://twitter.com/parenteau', :target => '_blank'}Michael Parenteau 
            &amp; Relevance, Inc. It’s built on Rails 3 and uses the swish gem. 
            The code is hosted on github and is ready for your design/dev love. 
            hooppps is in no way affiliated with dribbble but is obviously a huge fan! 
        %a#github.fadein{:href => "http://github.com/relevance/hooppps", :target => '_blank'} code on github
        %a#twitter.fadein{:href => "http://twitter.com/share?text=Check%20out%20@hooppps:%20a%20mobile%20@dribbble%20browser&url=http://hooppps.com", :target => '_blank'} share on twitter
        #relevance.footer
          Created by
          %a.fadein{:href => "http://thinkrelevance.com", :target => '_blank'} relevance
        #heroku.footer
          Hosted on
          %a.fadein{:href => "http://heroku.com", :target => '_blank'} heroku
